            <div class="about-text">
                <p>
                    Impact is a world-leading experiential learning company. Since 1980, we have worked with organizations to develop leadership capacity and catalyze change. We believe that organizations should be purpose-driven, human-centric places where people can thrive while making a positive impact in the world. We break down barriers that exist between sectors and industries to create meaningful social impact partnerships between companies, social sector organizations and the people that drive them. The common purpose of these connections: to deliver real value to each partner through innovations in community engagement, and ultimately to address deeply rooted and complex social challenges. We have a deep understanding of both mission-focused and business goals. Common Impact enables growing nonprofits to achieve even greater results in our communities while simultaneously engaging corporate employees in dynamic and challenging opportunities that develop their skills and unlock successful, purpose-driven careers.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact" >
        <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div class="section-header"><br>
                <h2><u>Contact us</u></h2><br>
